{"tid":1919123,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚德塞指中國疫情局勢逆轉　病毒正退卻","createTime":"2020-03-10T14:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T17:43:39.000Z","uid":39464,"like":16,"dislike":221,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"fddfa3b864dec71be6d1f1cc655de787241011f1","tid":1919123,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:33:43.000Z","msg":"世衛總幹事譚德塞說，中國近期的新型肺炎確診病例下降趨勢明顯，疫情局勢實現逆轉，病毒正在退卻，國際社會應該充分利用中國爭取的「機會窗口」，盡早遏制病毒傳播。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞重申，新冠病毒的傳染性很強，但仍然可以控制，全球要加強聯防聯控，尤其加強區域性國際組織的協同與合作。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，中國向世衛捐出2000萬美元，譚德塞說，捐款將支持衛生系統較弱的國家應對疫情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513644-20200310.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513644-20200310.htm&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=2be313a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513644-20200310.htm&h=358e3c7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513644-20200310.htm</a>"},{"pid":"edb2db81ef5fe9dffd413761adc959aa6f3223dd","tid":1919123,"uid":35456,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:35:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d95ade761c0df62a048b5b4b2216dc67e275bb3","tid":1919123,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e57e3e1e138348509c6c5cdcfc2988f7ec68d0","tid":1919123,"uid":309935,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:36:52.000Z","msg":"食啦"},{"pid":"ba9b2a7c4dd6295c9a51ecd48e37cc13c50e40bf","tid":1919123,"uid":236356,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:37:28.000Z","msg":"重點：又收多2000萬美元<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/d